{"name":"Indomitable","permission":{"default":0,"qtCGxlh91gcrIBBu":3},"type":"talent","data":{"description":"<h2>Tier 5</h2>\n<p>Once per encounter, when your character would be incapacitated due to exceeding their wound or strain threshold, you may spend a Story Point to use this talent. Then, your character is not incapacitated until the end of their next turn. If your character reduces their strain or wounds to below their threshold before the end of their next turn, they are not incapacitated.</p>","attributes":{},"activation":{"value":"Active (Incidental, Out of Turn)","type":"String","label":"Activation"},"ranks":{"ranked":false,"current":1,"min":0},"isForceTalent":false,"isConflictTalent":false,"tier":1,"trees":[]},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"44XKH09J8FUOGlo2"}
